data.description: Beautiful well maintained home built in 2016 located short distance from Mazda Toyota. New paint, 8ft fence covered backyard, pergola and wall mounted heater on back porch that conveys. Wainscoting in dining area. Crown molding throughout, granite countertops and wood flooring.
